title: Packers Top 5? Defensive duos, Patriots chances, Scott Pioli, and Vulnerable Division winners
itunes:title: Packers Top 5? Defensive duos, Patriots chances, Scott Pioli, and Vulnerable Division winners
description:
The Good Morning Football Podcast begins with questions around the Packers this season. Hosts Peter Schrager, Kyle Brandt, Jane Slater, and Super Bowl Champion Michael Robinson give their reasons for Green Bay being a Top 5 team or not.  We look at the best defensive duo coming in 2022 before asking if the Patriots will be compete for the AFC East.  Fmr NFL Exec Scott Pioli drops by with his thoughts on the Ravens Draft and how teams look at schedule releases. The table debates which Division winners will be vulnerable with Kyle and Peter explaining how both could come from this season's Super Bowl matchup.

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
